{"word":"ἀντηρίς","slug":"ἀντηρίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n9771\" key=\"a)nthri/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀντηρίς</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ίδος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n9771.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">prop, stay, support,</tr_> <bibl n=\"Eur. Fr. 1111\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1111</biblScope> </bibl>: pl., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:4:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.4.6</biblScope> </bibl>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stanchion</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">strut</tr_> in torsion-engines, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1599.tlg001:76:16\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Bel.\">Bel.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">76.16</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0559.tlg012:101:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hero\">Hero</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Bel.\">Bel.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">101.9</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀρκύων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg014.perseus-grc1:10:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyn.\">Cyn.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.7</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:36\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.36</biblScope> </bibl> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀντηρίδες</foreign> are <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stay-beams</tr_> fixed inside a ship's bow, and projecting beyond it, so as to support and strengthen the <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπωτίδες.</foreign> </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n9771.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\">=<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">θυρίς,</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">window,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Suid.</author> </bibl>:—and in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg019.perseus-grc1:785\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Rh.\">Rh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">785</biblScope> </bibl> it must mean <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">nostrils,</tr_> if it be the right reading. [<pron extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pron\">ῐδος</pron> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> </bibl> ll.cc.: hence <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀντήρειδες</foreign> in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1165.tlg001:178:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Apollod.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Poliorc.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">178.4</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0559.tlg012:101:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hero\">Hero</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Bel.\">Bel.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">101.9</biblScope></bibl>, is wrong; so <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-είδιον</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0559.tlg012:89:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">89.4</biblScope> </bibl> is <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">f.l. for</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">-ίδιον</ref> </xr> as Inscrr. show.] (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-ηρῐδ</foreign> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">-ερῐδ-</ref></xr>, weak form of stem of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐρείδω</foreign> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔρις</foreign>).)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}